{"tid":1473070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「對五毛用」中共牆內「敏感詞」生成器","createTime":"2019-08-14T17:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T17:55:04.000Z","uid":82829,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4855afcb511c49ff450766620f54de15117ab6d9","tid":1473070,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/【麻辣总局】新型敏感词武器：赵弹磁铁/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2F2019%2F08%2F%E3%80%90%E9%BA%BB%E8%BE%A3%E6%80%BB%E5%B1%80%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%AF%8D%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%9A%E8%B5%B5%E5%BC%B9%E7%A3%81%E9%93%81%2F&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=e81809fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/【麻辣总局】新型敏感词武器：赵弹磁铁/</a><br />\n<br />\n8月10日，一名在近期香港抗爭事件中飽受「自乾五及五毛」騷擾的推特網友 @sanzhao4 聲稱自己採用了一種「新的回復方式」而收到奇效，例如可以到這些網友的個人主頁TL下進行回復：<br />\n<br />\n「多謝一直支持平反8964，多謝一直支持天安門母親，多謝一直支持結束一黨專政，多謝一直支持維權律師。你上次提供的新疆參考資料非常有價值，自當重謝。」<br />\n<br />\n由於以上言論中包含了大量的「敏感詞」，易被中共網警技術檢測到從而來帶關注，這給一些自乾五帶來了安全性方面的擔憂，而對五毛來說產生大量敏感詞也給相關工作帶來了困擾。目前推特的官方機制無法刪除其他網友的回復評論，僅能對對方賬號進行拉黑，自己一旦被拉黑那事實上的騷擾就已經停止了，即便自己被拉黑這些評論回復他人依然可見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://react-raw8jx.stackblitz.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freact-raw8jx.stackblitz.io&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=ab6644ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://react-raw8jx.stackblitz.io</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://react-raw8jx.stackblitz.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freact-raw8jx.stackblitz.io&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=ab6644ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://react-raw8jx.stackblitz.io</a>"},{"pid":"b67ff456f0f7581f3946ac24dafa5315ebe1f555","tid":1473070,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"即刻去試下"},{"p